{"type": "article", "id": 29066, "title": "电水壶", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-04T05:10:56Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160704023844LT308KSH7PJrAoCa.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">城市中的居住空间越来越小了，这在皇家艺术学院毕业生 <a href=\"http://www.rca.ac.uk/students/keren-hu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Keren Hu</a> 看来，意味着通常会与他人共享空间的年轻人们将需要更多小巧且功能齐备的物件，为此他设计了一款桌上电水壶 Teawith，打破了客厅与厨房的边界，让人不再受限于灶台旁。水壶上方是一个铝制的提梁，弧形结构让握持变得更加舒适顺手，放下时只要按下提梁就能够开启烧水功能。无论是醒来后的第一杯水、办公桌上的一杯咖啡，还是两三好友相约的下午茶，Teawith 都可以满足日常需要，干净利落的外观让它不会再被冷落，可以大大方方地摆上桌面。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704024102lZLP9sDo7wHQEpOu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704024131PpFV2qZhWUNxvsr4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704024149ctzR3PeAnWOU8Jum.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704024221nYHzBdGUtxMkrl1b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}